# State Engine Framework – Roadmap

## v1.x – Core Templates

- [x] PST_v1.1 – Project State Template
- [x] SST_v1.0 – Search State Template
- [ ] CST_v1.0 – Coding State Template
- [ ] WST_v1.0 – Writing State Template
- [ ] DST_v1.0 – Data State Template
- [ ] RST_v1.0 – Research State Template
- [ ] TST_v1.0 – Trading State Template

## v2.x – Ecosystem

- [ ] Kaggle Dataset: `state-engine-templates`
- [ ] Kaggle Notebook: `state-engine-playground`
- [ ] Example gallery for each template
- [ ] Simple website / docs page (optional)

## Ideas

- Template Generator Template (TGT): a meta-template to help people design new State Templates.
- Integration examples for:
  - AI coding sessions (multi-file repos)
  - Story / novel writing workflows
  - Trading logs and scenario maps
  - Research / paper reading pipelines
